Articles.Content: I have several vessels with the Orbital assembly docking ports from KSP interstellar extended. Recently, however, these docking ports have lost the ability to undock from other vessels/payloads. I hit undock in the context menu, the undock button disappears and nothing undocks. I've tried looking into the save file data, but I don't know what I'm doing or what I'm looking for. Can anyone help?
